org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"a battle style\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"dance\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the 70s\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"a beat\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are three kinds of moves that appear to defy the laws of physics.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three kinds\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"moves\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"the laws\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"physics\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spins are power moves in a breaker's arsenal, where they balance on either their hands, even their heads.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spins\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"power moves\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"a breaker's arsenal\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"either their hands\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"even their heads\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The magic in this move is how the breaker generates and controls their speed with their legs.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The magic\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"this move\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaker\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"their speed\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"their legs\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kind of like how a figure skater speeds up when they move their arms in closer.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a figure\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"their arms\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In physics, this is called conservation of angular momentum.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"physics\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"angular momentum\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Floats are another kind of power move that has a ton of variations.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Floats\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"another kind\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"power move\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"a ton\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"variations\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For this move, the breaker uses their arms to seemingly float off the floor.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this move\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaker\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"their arms\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This requires a ton of core strength.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ton\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"core strength\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You thought planks were hard?\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"planks\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a good sense of knowing where their center of gravity is, or where their weight is evenly distributed.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And a good sense\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"their center\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"gravity\", \"f